\title{Kleene Star in \deplambek}
\date{2025-02-03T19:03:14Z}
\author{stevenschaefer}
\taxon{definition}
\tag{deplambek}

\import{grammar-macros}

\p{
  For a grammar #{A}, the Kleene star \star{A} is defined as a least-fixed point,

  ##{\lfp{x}{\epsilon \oplus \prn{A \otimes x}}}
}

\p{
  In \deplambek, it is derivable that #{\star{A} \cong \lfp{x}{\epsilon \oplus \prn{x \otimes A}}}.
}
